  "id" : "api/common/NgClass",
  "title" : "NgClass",
  "contents" : "<article>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"no-toc\" id=\"ngclass\">NgClass</h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label directive\">directive</label>\n    \n    \n    \n    <span class=\"version\"></span>\n  </header>\n\n  \n  <!-- INFO BAR -->\n<section class=\"info-bar\">\n\n<table class=\"is-full-width\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4wfc14obst93bim1zva6hqjl0\">npm 包</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/common\">@angular/common</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dkuxw56x8curh875ge5tvqede\">模块</th>\n  <td><code>import { <a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgClass</a> } from <a href=\"api/common\">'@angular/common'</a>;</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ee4tba1a8v4m1low7rnv25o9l\">源码</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/common/src/directives/ng_class.ts#L10-L158\">common/src/directives/ng_class.ts</a></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n  <th>NgModule</th>\n  <td><a href=\"api/common/CommonModule\"><code>CommonModule</code></a></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n<div class=\"what-it-does info-banner\">\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"rm8e4keowvkunvocplxwt4mn\">从 HTML 元素上添加和移除 CSS 类。</p>\n\n</div>\n\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"directive-overview\">\n  <h2 id=\"overview\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3ivgu86loww6mg4fq1brezlnd\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>概览</h2>\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>({ selector: '[<a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngClass</a>]' })\nclass <a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgClass</a> implements <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/DoCheck\">DoCheck</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/NgClass#klass\">set klass: string</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/NgClass#ngClass\">set ngClass: string | string[] | Set&lt;string&gt; | {...}</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/NgClass#ngDoCheck\">ngDoCheck(): void</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n</section>\n\n  \n<section class=\"how-to-use\">\n  <h2 id=\"how-to-use\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cflu95twzi71qd095ghj9h0y7\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>使用方法</h2>\n  <code-example>\n    &lt;some-element [<a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngClass</a>]=\"'first second'\"&gt;...&lt;/some-element&gt;\n\n    &lt;some-element [<a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngClass</a>]=\"['first', 'second']\"&gt;...&lt;/some-element&gt;\n\n    &lt;some-element [<a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngClass</a>]=\"{'first': true, 'second': true, 'third': false}\"&gt;...&lt;/some-element&gt;\n\n    &lt;some-element [<a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngClass</a>]=\"stringExp|arrayExp|objExp\"&gt;...&lt;/some-element&gt;\n\n    &lt;some-element [<a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngClass</a>]=\"{'class1 class2 class3' : true}\"&gt;...&lt;/some-element&gt;\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n<section class=\"selectors\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2ukliajrgrqzf6qt0k49ld9w9\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>选择器</h2>\n  <code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading selector\">\n  [<a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngClass</a>]\n  </code-example>\n</section>\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"inputs\">\n  <h2 id=\"inputs\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e41z1ta8j4fn0xhay00whz365\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>输入</h2>\n  \n  <div class=\"input\">\n    <code>class</code>&nbsp;bound to&nbsp;<code><a href=\"api/common/NgClass#klass\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgClass.klass</a></code>\n    \n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"input\">\n    <code><a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngClass</a></code>&nbsp;bound to&nbsp;<code><a href=\"api/common/NgClass#ngClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgClass.ngClass</a></code>\n    \n  </div>\n  \n</section>\n\n  \n  \n\n\n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ar5q09mdsagdppsbze96eagxl\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>说明</h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5sj811f5n2vglv0y7cjlj9ntw\">CSS 类会根据表达式求值结果进行更新，更新逻辑取决于结果的类型：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bce5wjxhu5rqutsxnc9ek2o9w\"><code>string</code> - 会把列在字符串中的 CSS 类（空格分隔）添加进来，</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8hrnvfbpv86gec08b8k901wn4\"><code>Array</code> - 会把数组中的各个元素作为 CSS 类添加进来，</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"d3o6bsef8u7o5hm3j08cvdlmh\"><code>Object</code> - 键是 CSS 类，当值中给出的表达式 求值为真值时，这些类将被添加，否则将被删除。</li>\n</ul>\n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"constructors\">\n  <h2 id=\"constructor\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"64p310lbzdqiret0qyhhannvq\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>构造函数</h2>\n  \n    <div class=\"constructor\">\n  <a id=\"constructor()\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">constructor(_iterableDiffers: <a href=\"api/core/IterableDiffers\" class=\"code-anchor\">IterableDiffers</a>, _keyValueDiffers: <a href=\"api/core/KeyValueDiffers\" class=\"code-anchor\">KeyValueDiffers</a>, _ngEl: <a href=\"api/core/ElementRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">ElementRef</a>, _renderer: <a href=\"api/core/Renderer2\" class=\"code-anchor\">Renderer2</a>)</code-example></div>\n\n    \n    \n  \n</section>\n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"instance-members\">\n  <h2 id=\"members\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e62kgm2ztk7rgk6auybfiv91o\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>成员</h2>\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"klass\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">set klass: string</code-example></div>\n\n    \n    <hr class=\"hr-margin\">\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"ngClass\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">set <a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngClass</a>: string | string[] | Set&lt;string&gt; | {\n    [klass: string]: any;\n}</code-example></div>\n\n    \n    <hr class=\"hr-margin\">\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"ngDoCheck\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">ngDoCheck(): void</code-example></div>\n\n    \n    \n  \n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</section></article>\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - guide/ajs-quick-reference\n - guide/browser-support\n - guide/glossary\n - guide/structural-directives\n - guide/template-syntax\n - guide/upgrade\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/CommonModule\n - api/common/NgClass#constructor\n - api/common/NgClass#description\n - api/common/NgClass#how-to-use\n - api/common/NgClass#inputs\n - api/common/NgClass#klass\n - api/common/NgClass#members\n - api/common/NgClass#ngClass\n - api/common/NgClass#ngDoCheck\n - api/common/NgClass#ngclass\n - api/common/NgClass#overview\n - api/common/NgClass#selectors\n - api/core/Directive\n - api/core/DoCheck\n - api/core/ElementRef\n - api/core/IterableDiffers\n - api/core/KeyValueDiffers\n - api/core/Renderer2\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/common/src/directives/ng_class.ts#L10-L158\n - https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/common\n-->"
